705188f-a.title: Brooklyn: Kent Avenue - 9th Street (South)
705188f-a.text:
Kent Avenue, north irom South 9th Street toward the 'illiamsburg
Bridge. At the northeast corner of South 8th Street is the
Harris paint factory. This building, and others extending to
Broadway, can be seen in view 2.
P. L. Sperr  Spril 11, 1931
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
